  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_The Wall Street Journal - 2025-01-08@magazinesclubnew_page_018_18",
    "text": "in NYC is significant,\" he said. City and state transporta- tion officials say truckers can reduce costs by delivering overnight. The congestion toll for heavy-duty trucks drops to $5.40 during off-peak hours.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.8330146590184832,
      0.24954245245484205,
      0.9853409815168898,
      0.30142436540144824
    ],
    "page": "newspaper_The Wall Street Journal - 2025-01-08@magazinesclubnew_page_018",
    "order": 9
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_newspaper_The Wall Street Journal - 2025-01-08@magazinesclubnew_page_018_10",
    "text": "Freight companies and their customers say the charges will pile on costs for cargo that can't reach its des- tination any other way.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.5041427660930529,
      0.2501790403437575,
